NAME
    DBIx::Class::Schema::Critic - Critique a database schema for best
    practices

VERSION
    version 0.001

USAGE
        dbic-critic --help
        dbic-critic --dsn dbi:Oracle:HR --username scott --password tiger

DESCRIPTION
    This is the command line interface to DBIx::Class::Schema::Critic, a
    utility for scanning a database schema for violations of best practices.

CONFIGURATION
    Any command line options can also be specified in a configuration file
    and loaded with the *--configfile* option as per MooseX::SimpleConfig.

SUPPORT
  Perldoc
    You can find documentation for this module with the perldoc command.

      perldoc bin::dbic_critic

